# IT Projects Repository

Welcome to your IT Projects Repository! This repository contains beginner-friendly IT projects designed to help you build foundational skills in various areas such as networking, system administration, cybersecurity, 
and more.

## Table of Contents

1. [Help Desk and IT Support Projects](#help-desk-and-it-support-projects)
2. [Networking Projects](#networking-projects)
3. [System Administration Projects](#system-administration-projects)
4. [Cybersecurity Projects](#cybersecurity-projects)
5. [Cloud and Virtualization Projects](#cloud-and-virtualization-projects)
6. [Hardware and Repair Projects](#hardware-and-repair-projects)
7. [Documentation and Presentation](#documentation-and-presentation)
8. [Programming Basics](#programming-basics)

